info.name: Metis plus bedside chest
info.description: Precious high gloss grey, white and sand surfaces give METIS plus its distinctive look. The light-hearted design works both in a single colour and with a mix of colours. Core walnut or natural oak add a natural, contrasting version. The accent colour high-gloss violett provides an exciting visual impact and completes the fabulous METIS plus colour composition. Many beautiful fabrics are available in METIS plus.
